Council of High Intelligence — Gemini CLI Port
===============================================

This project is a Gemini CLI port of the Council of High Intelligence
by @0xNyk (https://github.com/0xNyk/council-of-high-intelligence).

The persona definitions, deliberation protocol, triad taxonomy, polarity
pairs, enforcement rules, and verdict templates are derived from the
original work and used under the MIT License.

Original repository: https://github.com/0xNyk/council-of-high-intelligence
Original author:     @0xNyk
License:             MIT (see LICENSE)

Modifications in this port:
- Translated from Claude Code extension format to Gemini CLI extension format
- Replaced Claude subagent spawning with Gemini sub-agent persona embodiment
- Replaced detect-providers.sh auto-routing with native MCP server routing
- Added configs/mcp-provider-slots.yaml for MCP-based multi-provider deliberation
- Extended install.sh with --gemini / --gemini-only / --all targets
- Extracted triad taxonomy and verdict templates to progressive reference files
